parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Leak and Fuel Vapor Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel leak and fuel vapor ingress can cause a strong smell of gasoline in the cabin, posing a fire hazard and potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Strong smell of gasoline in the cabin
especially after filling the fuel tank
fuel leak at the fuel sending unit/pump
fuel odor outside the car after stopping
fuel odor persists until approximately 1/8 tank of gasoline is used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the SBC system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: red warning sign on the dashboard saying "Brake Malfunction Stop Vehicle"
SBC pump smoking from the hood
and excessive heat from the pump.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Defective Wiring Harness for Tail Light Board
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty wiring harness for the tail light board can cause the brake lights, night lights, signal lights, and reverse lights to malfunction or fail, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: or reverse lights do not function or malfunction intermittently
the lights may flicker or dim
the lights may not turn on at all
or the lights may stay on continuously.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Leaks and Component Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system leaks and component failure can cause fuel to leak, leading to a fire hazard, and inaccurate fuel level readings, which can cause the vehicle to run out of fuel unexpectedly, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: fuel leaks when filling the tank

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inaccurate fuel level readings can cause the vehicle to run out of fuel unexpectedly, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: vehicle running out of fuel unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel pump assembly failure can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls or does not start

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air suspension system can cause uneven ride height, reduced vehicle stability, and increased risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or carrying heavy loads.
symptoms: Warning lights illuminate on the dashboard indicating low air pressure
unusual noises or vibrations while driving.
